{"tid":702954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"腳指公外側痛到仆街","createTime":"2018-06-15T10:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T12:18:37.000Z","uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf79960069d4382d8d718cb627359b3ed6c1dbd","tid":702954,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/182949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F182949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=32701433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依個位痛到傻，平時行路唔痛，但如果禁落去就痛到眼水都標出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔係啲指甲生左入肉，我已經嘗試用指甲鉗整出嚟，但都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明顯見到圈住個位有紅腫，同埋頭先整佢果陣有膿出。<br />\n手痕試下禁一下，痛到嗌救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依啲情況係咪要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：已經用酒精抺洗膿個位"},{"pid":"8034377545dfde6e872ab0ba2299d1f80d0414e7","tid":702954,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<br />\n重上child登問"},{"pid":"a5917ff3caf38e10d59ae23bdde92d6f38735f62","tid":702954,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"睇公立拎referral 去睇足科<br />\n<br />\n大嘅會咁做<br />\n係腳趾神經打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n𠝹開放濃"},{"pid":"9143a8ec690415eba88527c7f1c6b04dcc6367f3","tid":702954,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8034377545dfde6e872ab0ba2299d1f80d0414e7","tid":702954,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:40:05.0